        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>Genesis 2</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Gen002-P6r-L12" n="12"
                            prev="JSul.IV.02A.001.001.xml#Gen001-P6r-L12" />
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Gen-002-001">Da täkmillendilär ol gök da ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            jer da ǯümlä čerivläri.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Gen-002-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויכל </foreign>
                            Da tekmil idti Täŋri ol je<supplied reason="lost">d</supplied>inǯi<ref
                                n="1" target="#Gen-002-fn1" type="noteAnchor" /> gündä išin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ki jaradty da qaldy ol jedinǯi gündä ǯümlä išindän ki jaradty.</l>
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Gen-002-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ךְויבר</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            Da alɣyšlady Täŋri ol jedinǯi günni da ajruqsu idti any zira onda qaldy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            ǯümlä išindän ki jaradty Täŋri qylmadan.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Gen-002-004"><ref n="2" target="#Gen-002-fn2"
                                type="noteAnchor" /><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ב </foreign>
                            Bulardyrlar ḥäkijätläri ol gökniŋ da ol jerniŋ jaratylɣanlaryndan soŋra
                                jara<supplied reason="lost">tq</supplied>an<ref n="3"
                                target="#Gen-002-fn3" type="noteAnchor" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            vaqytdan soŋra YWY Täŋri jerni da gökni.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Gen-002-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ובל </foreign>
                            Da ǯümlä d<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>rägi<ref n="4"
                                target="#Gen-002-fn4" type="noteAnchor" /> ol düzniŋ burun
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            olur edi jerdä da ǯümlä otu ol düzniŋ burun bitär edi farzam
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            jaɣdyrmajyp edi YWY Tänri jaɣmur ol jer üstünä da adamda joq edi išlämä
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            ol jerni.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Gen-002-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואד </foreign>
                            Da buḫar čyqar edi ol jerdän da suvaryr edi ǯümlä jüzlärin ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            jerniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Gen-002-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצר </foreign>
                            Da jaradty YWY Täŋri ol adamny topraq ol jerdän da üfürdi burnyna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            näfäsin dirlikniŋ da oldu ol adam diri ǯanɣa.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Gen-002-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויטע </foreign>
                            Da dikti YWY Täŋri baḫča
                            <milestone unit="page" n="6v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            ʿEdende evveldän<ref n="5" target="#Gen-002-fn5" type="noteAnchor" /> da
                            qojdy orada ol adamny ki jaradty.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Gen-002-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצמח </foreign>
                            D<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied><ref n="6" target="#Gen-002-fn6"
                                type="noteAnchor" /> evvel
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            bittirdi YWY Täŋri ol jerdän ǯümlä suqlančly aɣačny görmägä da jaḫšyny ašamaɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            da aɣačyn ol dirlikniŋ ortasynda ol baḫčanyŋ da aɣačyn ol bilmäkniŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            bilmägä jaḫšyny da jamanny.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Gen-002-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ונהר </foreign>
                            Da özek čyqar edi ʿEdendän suvarmaɣa ol baḫča-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            ny da oradan ajyrylyr edi da olur edi dört bašlarɣa.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Gen-002-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שׁם </foreign>
                            Ady ol birsiniŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            Pišon oldyr ol dolašqan ǯümlä jerin ol dolašqan ǯümlä jerin ol Ḥavilanyŋ
                            ki oradadyr ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            altyn.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Gen-002-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וזהב </foreign>
                            Da altyny ol jerniŋ jaḫšydyr oradadyr ol inǯi da ol šoham
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            dašy</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Gen-002-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושׁמ </foreign>
                            Da ady ol ekinǯi özenniŋ Giḥon oldyr ol dolašqan ǯümlä
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            Kušnyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Gen-002-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושׁם </foreign>
                            Da ady ol üčünǯi özenniŋ Ḥideqel oldyr ol varɣan gün doɣušyna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            Ašurnyŋ da ol dördinǯi özen oldyr Perat.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Gen-002-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקח </foreign>
                            Da aldy YWY Täŋri ol adam-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            ny da qojdy any ɣanimetli baḫčada išlämägä any da saqlamaɣa any.</l>
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Gen-002-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצו</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            Da symarlap tenbäḥ idti YWY Täŋri ol adamɣa demä ǯümlä aɣačyndan ol baḫčanyŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            ašama ašaɣyn.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Gen-002-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ומעץ </foreign>
                            Da aɣačyndan ol bilmäkniŋ bilmägä jaḫšyny da jamanny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ašamaɣyn ondan zira ašadyɣyŋ günüŋdän soŋra ondan ülmä ülärsin.</l>
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Gen-002-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            Da ajtty YWY Täŋri jaḫšy dügüldir olma ol adam jalynɣyz qylajym oŋa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            bolušluq qaršysyna.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Gen-002-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצר </foreign>
                            Da jaradty YWY Täŋri ol jerdän ǯümlä kijigin ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            düzniŋ da ol ǯümlä qušun ol gökniŋ da getirdi ol adamɣa görmägä ne
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            atar oŋa da her ad ki atasa oŋa ol adam diri ǯanɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            ol olyr ady.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Gen-002-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da atady ol adam adlar ǯümlä ol tuvarɣa da qušuna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            ol gökniŋ da ǯümlä kijiginä ol düzniŋ da Adam gendine bulmady bolušluq
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            qaršysyna.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Gen-002-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויפל </foreign>
                            Da düšürdi YWY Täŋri derän juḫu ol adam üstünä da juḥlady
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            da aldy birni qaburɣalaryndan da beklädi et onyŋ jerinä</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Gen-002-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy YWY Täŋri
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ol qaburɣadan ki aldy ol adamdan ḫatynny da getirdi any ol adamɣa.</l>
                        <milestone unit="page" n="7r" />
                        <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                        <l n="23" xml:id="Gen-002-023"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol adam bu ol vaqyt süjäktir süjäklärimdän da et-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            tir etimdän buŋa atalyr ḫatyn zire erdän alyndy bu.</l>
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Gen-002-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">על </foreign>
                            Anyŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            učun kemišir kiši atasyny da anasyny da japušur ḫatynyna da olurlar bir tän-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            gä.</l>
                        <l n="25" xml:id="Gen-002-025"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויהיו </foreign>
                            Da edilär ekisi čyplaqlar ol adam da ḫatyny da ujalmaz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            edilär.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-002-fn1" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A:
                            <emph>jerinǯi</emph>; a scribal error. | BSMS 288: <emph>jedinǯi</emph>.
                            | ADub.III.73: <emph>jedinči</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-002-fn2" type="footnote">The chapter number (2) is written
                            in a wrong place.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-002-fn3" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A:
                                <emph>jaraqtan</emph>; a scribal error. | BSMS 288:
                                <emph>jaratqan</emph>. | ADub.III.73: <emph>jaratqan</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-002-fn4" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: <emph>dirägi</emph>;
                            probably a scribal error. | BSMS 288: <emph>terägi</emph>. |
                            ADub.III.73: <emph>teregi</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-002-fn5" type="footnote">The Biblical Hebrew <foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מִקֶּדֶם </foreign>
                            has multiple meanings, e.g. ‘from the front; from the east; for the
                            first time; from of old’ (Koehler &amp; Baumgartner 1985: 823–824) while
                            it stands for ‘eastward’ in Gen 2:8. However, in JSul.IV.02A this word
                            is denoted by <emph>evveldän </emph>‘from of old/first (time)’. This
                            mistranslation was repeated in several Karaim manuscripts and has
                            already been remarked by Henderson (1826: 336). |BSMS 288:
                                <emph>äväldä</emph>. | ADub.III.73: <emph>burundan</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-002-fn6" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: <emph>de</emph>; a
                            scribal error. | BSMS 288: <emph>da</emph>. | ADub.III.73:
                                <emph>da</emph>.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
